== 製作 ==
=== 開發與製作 ===
2013年8月6日，[[HBO|HBO]]宣布開發由{{link-en|依莎·蕾|Issa Rae}}與{{link-en|賴瑞·威摩爾|Larry Wilmore}}共同開創的新喜劇試播集，講述一名[[非裔美國人|非裔]]女子於今代生活的尷尬日常，並由依莎·蕾主演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/08/hbo-developing-comedy-series-from-larry-wilmore-issa-rae-to-star-rae-557790/|title=HBO Developing Comedy Series From Larry Wilmore & Issa Rae To Star Rae|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2013-08-06|accessdate=2016-10-10|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005109/https://deadline.com/2013/08/hbo-developing-comedy-series-from-larry-wilmore-issa-rae-to-star-rae-557790/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年2月4日，HBO正式預訂本劇試播集，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/issa-rae-comedy-insecure-pilot-order-hbo-1201366166/|title=Issa Rae Comedy Gets HBO Pilot Order|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2015-02-04|accessdate=2016-10-10|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001074123/https://deadline.com/2015/02/issa-rae-comedy-insecure-pilot-order-hbo-1201366166/|dead-url=no}}</ref>並由[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]導演{{link-en|梅琳娜·馬特索卡斯|Melina Matsoukas}}執導。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/issa-rae-insecure-hbo-comedy-pilot-melina-masoukas-direct-1201459517/|title=HBO’s Issa Rae Comedy Pilot: Music Video Helmer Melina Matsoukas To Direct|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2015-06-26|accessdate=2016-10-10|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212085251/https://deadline.com/2015/06/issa-rae-insecure-hbo-comedy-pilot-melina-masoukas-direct-1201459517/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月6日，宣布由於威摩爾尚執掌自己於[[喜劇中心|喜劇中心]]的深夜秀《{{link-en|賴瑞·威摩爾每夜秀|The Nightly Show with Larry Wilmore}}》，因此將由《[[神煩警察|荒唐分局]]》普倫提斯·潘尼（{{lang|en|Prentice Penny}}）出任節目主理人，並與麥可·羅頓柏格（{{lang|en|Michael Rotenberg}}）、{{le|戴夫·貝奇|Dave Becky}}與喬納森·貝瑞（{{lang|en|Jonathan Berry}}）共同擔任執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/insecure-prentice-penny-showrunner-hbo-pilot-1201467571/|title=HBO Comedy Pilot ‘Insecure’ Taps Prentice Penny As Showrunner|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2015-07-06|accessdate=2016-10-10|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212043739/https://deadline.com/2015/07/insecure-prentice-penny-showrunner-hbo-pilot-1201467571/|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月15日，HBO正式系列預訂本劇。<ref name="Series Order">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/issa-rae-insecure-comedy-series-hbo-1201584383/|title=Issa Rae Comedy ‘Insecure’ Gets HBO Series Order|work=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2015-10-15|accessdate=2016-10-10|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108160803/https://deadline.com/2015/10/issa-rae-insecure-comedy-series-hbo-1201584383/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

蕾與節目主理人潘尼及執行製作馬特索卡斯於2016年HBO在[[電視評論家協會|電視評論家協會]]的訪談中談論本劇，蕾說道本劇將探討：「你無法逃避黑人身分的黑暗與真實之複雜性」，蕾亦說道考慮將潛在的主流意識反映到劇集上：「我們只是想試著傳達有色人種的關聯性。這不是包裹糖衣的故事。這是一般人的日常生活。」<ref name="Times">{{Cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-hbo-insecure-20160730-snap-story.html|title=Issa Rae takes HBO from white 'Girls' to black women with 'Insecure'|author=Greg Braxton|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|access-date=2016-08-28|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203003759/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-hbo-insecure-20160730-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

據[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的報導，第一季8集將以創新與真實的方式，來探討黑人女性的經驗。依莎，就如我們一般，試著找出她所想要的人生，同時思考著該如何去控制它，而莫莉則是個成功的法人律師，但她試著找出修補自己人生的方法。除了聚焦兩人的娛樂生活，這部半小時影集還包括各式各樣來自知名藝術家的流行音樂，並涉及當代黑人於社會與種族上之議題的經驗。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/insecure-teaser-issa-rae-hbo-comedy-series-1201720766/|title=‘Insecure’ Teaser: Issa Rae Is Torn Between Two Lovers In New HBO Comedy|last=Calvario|first=Liz|date=2016-08-26|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|access-date=2016-08-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108121854/https://www.indiewire.com/2016/08/insecure-teaser-issa-rae-hbo-comedy-series-1201720766/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年11月14日，HBO宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="Season 2 Renew">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/westworld-divorce-insecure-renewed-season-2-hbo-1201853994/|title=‘Westworld’, ‘Divorce’ & ‘Insecure’ Renewed For Season 2 By HBO|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=2016-11-14|accessdate=2016-11-14|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114225411/http://deadline.com/2016/11/westworld-divorce-insecure-renewed-season-2-hbo-1201853994/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年8月8日，HBO宣布續訂第3季。<ref name="Season 3 Renew">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/insecure-ballers-renewed-hbo-1202519373/|title=‘Insecure,’ ‘Ballers’ Renewed at HBO|website=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Joe Otterson|date=2017-08-08|accessdate=2017-08-08|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041917/https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/insecure-ballers-renewed-hbo-1202519373/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

